                           <li><i class="fa fa-check-square"></i>Video games were my hobby before finding coding. I want to be the best at whatever I do and have a hard work ethic to achieve that.</li>
                           <li><i class="fa fa-check-square"></i>Working on projects for long periods of time is something I am used to doing from creating art.</li>
                           <li><i class="fa fa-check-square"></i>I have lots of patienece that I am able to use when learning new things as well as understanding people!</li>
